Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是脑筋急转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现代国语的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是…寂静？
